  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race, outplay, destroy! Outrunner: Neon Nights blends high-speed arcade racing with tactical light trails. Challenge your friends and compete online with up to 8 players in gravity-defying arenas. Master power-ups and diverse game modes to take the lead.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defy gravity</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1439980/extras/7943803376684459557352429250b6d8.poster.avif?t=1739818927\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1439980/extras/7943803376684459557352429250b6d8.webm?t=1739818927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1439980/extras/7943803376684459557352429250b6d8.mp4?t=1739818927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the thrill of defying gravity as you race through futuristic landscapes. Perform wild jumps and navigate mind-bending environments where gravity is no longer bound to a single direction.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Outsmart your opponents</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1439980/extras/ed82de604b755ed882ad1923fe87e6c4.poster.avif?t=1739818927\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1439980/extras/ed82de604b755ed882ad1923fe87e6c4.webm?t=1739818927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1439980/extras/ed82de604b755ed882ad1923fe87e6c4.mp4?t=1739818927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Outplay your opponents with a variety of power-ups that give you the edge. Use speed boosts to surge ahead, trail-clearing abilities to disrupt your rivals, or widen your line for surprise attacks. The game rewards both skill and strategy as you balance speed, precision, and clever use of power-ups.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Online Multiplayer & Local Split screen</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1439980/extras/6a748663fbc7c69d4358f90e1f9b68df.poster.avif?t=1739818927\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1439980/extras/6a748663fbc7c69d4358f90e1f9b68df.webm?t=1739818927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1439980/extras/6a748663fbc7c69d4358f90e1f9b68df.mp4?t=1739818927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete online with up to 8 players or challenge a friend in local split-screen. Test your skills in fast-paced races and prove who truly dominates the neon track.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong>: Race and trap rivals with your light trail in fast, tactical races.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The World</strong>: Gravity-defying synthwave arenas.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiplayer</strong>: Online races with up to 8 players or local split-screen.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Maps & Gravity</strong>: 7 Diverse maps.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Modes & Power-ups</strong>: Use power-ups to outsmart opponents in various modes.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Credits</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trailer Music: \"Technology 82\" by Zodik. Available for use under the CC BY 3.0 license</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race, outplay, destroy! Outrunner: Neon Nights blends high-speed arcade racing with tactical light trails. Challenge your friends and compete online with up to 8 players in gravity-defying arenas. Master power-ups and diverse game modes to take the lead.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defy gravity</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1439980/extras/7943803376684459557352429250b6d8.poster.avif?t=1739818927\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1439980/extras/7943803376684459557352429250b6d8.webm?t=1739818927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1439980/extras/7943803376684459557352429250b6d8.mp4?t=1739818927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the thrill of defying gravity as you race through futuristic landscapes. Perform wild jumps and navigate mind-bending environments where gravity is no longer bound to a single direction.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Outsmart your opponents</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1439980/extras/ed82de604b755ed882ad1923fe87e6c4.poster.avif?t=1739818927\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1439980/extras/ed82de604b755ed882ad1923fe87e6c4.webm?t=1739818927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1439980/extras/ed82de604b755ed882ad1923fe87e6c4.mp4?t=1739818927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Outplay your opponents with a variety of power-ups that give you the edge. Use speed boosts to surge ahead, trail-clearing abilities to disrupt your rivals, or widen your line for surprise attacks. The game rewards both skill and strategy as you balance speed, precision, and clever use of power-ups.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Online Multiplayer & Local Split screen</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1439980/extras/6a748663fbc7c69d4358f90e1f9b68df.poster.avif?t=1739818927\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1439980/extras/6a748663fbc7c69d4358f90e1f9b68df.webm?t=1739818927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1439980/extras/6a748663fbc7c69d4358f90e1f9b68df.mp4?t=1739818927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete online with up to 8 players or challenge a friend in local split-screen. Test your skills in fast-paced races and prove who truly dominates the neon track.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong>: Race and trap rivals with your light trail in fast, tactical races.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The World</strong>: Gravity-defying synthwave arenas.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiplayer</strong>: Online races with up to 8 players or local split-screen.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Maps & Gravity</strong>: 7 Diverse maps.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Modes & Power-ups</strong>: Use power-ups to outsmart opponents in various modes.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Credits</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trailer Music: \"Technology 82\" by Zodik. Available for use under the CC BY 3.0 license</p>",
